{"tid":1887932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2020年2月20日 — 早晨，Twitter戰線需要大家","createTime":"2020-02-20T01:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T15:53:35.000Z","uid":253983,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fe1a71d489ec1f9c424f3758e1ebe5ce7b09e7d8","tid":1887932,"uid":253983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T01:40:22.000Z","msg":"尋日包機嗰單嘢，真係覺得世上應該無比港共同中共更可恥嘅人形生物<br />\n<br />\n憤怒嗎？記住你嘅憤怒，亦要記住將憤怒轉化成抗爭嘅動力<br />\n嚟啦，喺Twitter戰線盡情出力啦！<br />\n<br />\n呢度有個今日任務嘅匯集，大家可以㩒呢條link入今日嘅任務<br />\n記得 Like + Retweet <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">原Tweet</span></span> 呀 <br />\n(總係有朋友仔Like + Tweet我地個comment就算，係要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">㩒入去原Tweet先Like + Retweet</span></span>呀)<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tweetingforhk/status/1230299367992590343?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftweetingforhk%2Fstatus%2F1230299367992590343%3Fs%3D21&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5LTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=d8ec0c86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftweetingforhk%2Fstatus%2F1230299367992590343%3Fs%3D21&h=9a05e48c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tweetingforhk/status/1230299367992590343?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，本站現新增簽名戰線，附上各項聯署任務，歡迎各位加入<br />\n<br />\n另外歡迎大家follow本站Twitter，留意每日Twitter戰線任務<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTweetingforHK&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5LTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=0da5c065\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK</a>"},{"pid":"653e649d78a4169229783e9977334165cf0217f2","tid":1887932,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T01:43:53.000Z","msg":"Twitter 用英文會唔會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw<br />\n當香港人仲掛住排口罩 搶廁紙 討論邊個邊個ig女神<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1887691\"